message.body: Hey, ill have those lights tonight if you want to grab them or something.
That would be really awesome. :)
K, ill let you know I have them later
Okay! How are ye?
I'm doing alright, how have you been?
Best I've been in a long time. :) living on my own, working a lot, getting super strong, I feel great. How come just alright?

That's awesome run emc! Are you getting to enjoy summer with all the work? You all ready for waka? Eh, just kind of trying to find my way through everything I guess. How'd that for q super melodramatic answer?@

Run emc hahahahaha I miss you. Oh I'm definitely enjoying summer!! Waka is going to be pure enjoyment. That's not melodramatic! Just honest. Important to own where you're at. What sort of stuff are you trying to find your way through?

When are you guys leaving? I'm super jealous, camping sounds fun. Kind of just the transition I'm in I guess. Really don't feel like I have a real connection with anyone and I'm becoming more insecure because of it. It'll all pan out@
Tomorrow at 6 am haha OMG OMG OMG OMG OmOmg I'm excited. Yeah I understand that. But it will work out, and you can do things to help it too. :)
Hahaha, the road trip will be so fun too. O don't I know it, Its a good time to kind of look at myself and figure my shit out. Just frustrating some time. I've got the lights meow.
Fuuuuck yeah!!!! I feel that completely. I've definitely had to do the same. Yay! Can I come get them?
You're a good role model then! Yes, ill be up for another hour or so
Okay weeeee!!! Thanks!
If you're gonna be later lemme know and ill set em out on the door step
No I'm leaving right now!
Allllright
￼Also would be a good place to stash.
￼Cool sign Walter made.
Is that for you camp site or is it a totem thing for walking around?
Both!!! Help us find each other too ^.^ and we have a colorado flag too.
That's a good idea! Go co pride! Are you guys there yet?
Hahaha no we aren't even out of colorado yet. We won't be there till way later tonight it's like 11 hours and we had to go to Denver to pick up Pat and that was hella traffic this morning.
Thanks a lot pat
Hahaha no he's cool. I just blew everyone's mind with the mantis shrimp.
Sherbert death bug. I would not be able to swim fast enough away if I saw a 1foot rainbow assassin lobster.
Hahahahaha so fucking crazy and awesome and I want to see it but also never
We agree on that then. O mother nature
I'm gonna say it, the lineup for global this year kinda seems weak.
Yeah I feel the same!!!! Not impressed. Not even sure if I'm gonna go.
I'm going to pretty lights :D
I unfortunately bought tickets assuming they would turn things around.
That'll be fun
Sell em? Fuuuuckkk yeah!
Probably will try. The last two years were so awesome, I'm surprised they seem to be going in a different direction.
Yeah I'm sure it'll be fun no matter what.
For shore. Hard to have a bad time at red rocks in the summer
Most definitely impossible.
Who are you really excited to see at waka?

Everyone OMG sound tribe of course, umphreys McGee, tipper, yonder mountain string band, dispatch, widespread panic, griz, gramatik, RJD2, Zion I, wick-it, boombox, shpongle, papadosio, snoop dogg... Hahah just everyone seriously it's going to be incredible.
Haha I know half of them. Justin talks about a lot of those bands I feel like
Yeah they are all incredible. If you're looking for new music, look any of those up.
Im really excited to find new music just cruising around at edc too. I'll give some if those guys a listen as well
Dooooo it!!!
